body:
Hello,

I'm trying to access the statistics via the API `/api/v1/statistic/by-date`.
Documentation seem clear https://documentation.mosparo.io/docs/api/statistic but not work for me.

To reproduce, i use instruction from documentation with this php script (replace public key and private key by project API keys) : 
```
<?php

$publicKey = 'REDACTED';
$privateKey = 'REDACTED';
$apiEndpoint = '/api/v1/statistic/by-date';
$formData = [];

$hmacHash = hash_hmac('sha256', $apiEndpoint . json_encode($formData), $privateKey);
$authHeader = base64_encode($publicKey . ':' . $hmacHash);

print_r($authHeader);
echo "\n";

?>
```

Result not show expected HmacHash.

Curl result show debug information reason `hmac_hash_invalid`
```
curl https://MOSPARO_URL/api/v1/statistic/by-date -H "Authorization: REDACTED" | jq .
```


I don't know if this is good practice.

Thanks,
Zulf
